{"id":2358,"date":"2025-10-14T02:40:45","date_gmt":"2025-10-14T02:40:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/?page_id=2358"},"modified":"2025-12-03T12:37:21","modified_gmt":"2025-12-03T12:37:21","slug":"certificazione-npack","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/it\/about-us\/npack-certification","title":{"rendered":"Certificazioni Npack"},"content":{"rendered":"<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"2358\" class=\"elementor elementor-2358\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4b9d536 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4b9d536\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-acaf631 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"acaf631\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>La nostra societ\u00e0 \u00e8 registrata ufficialmente come Shanghai Npack Automation Equipment Co., Ltd., che funge contemporaneamente da marchio.\n\nPanoramica del sistema di certificazione\nDurante ricerche su \"NPACK\", fare sempre riferimento alla ragione sociale completa. Tutte le certificazioni sono emesse a nome legale, garantendo autenticit\u00e0 e conformit\u00e0 dei prodotti.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20b5fe3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-shortcode\" data-id=\"20b5fe3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"shortcode.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-shortcode\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1732e38 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1732e38\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6060827 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6060827\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4949c21 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"4949c21\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img alt=\"Certificazione Npack - Macchina di riempimento liquidi della Cina Fornitore principale\" title=\"Certificazione Npack - Macchina di riempimento liquidi della Cina Fornitore principale\" fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"597\" height=\"824\" src=\"https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/2025101402434617.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-2364 wp-post-image\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-80654fe e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"80654fe\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ddc2327 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ddc2327\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Il Nostro Certificato di Registrazione del Marchio<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d573931 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"d573931\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9db9d92 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9db9d92\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Il marchio Npack \u00e8 registrato ufficialmente in tre mercati chiave: Stati Uniti, Europa e Cina. Questa strategia riflette il nostro impegno verso equipaggiamenti conformi agli standard normativi di queste aree. Proteggendo la nostra presenza in questi mercati, consolidiamo la nostra reputazione di partner affidabile a livello globale.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-40e5dde elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"40e5dde\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7e98049 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7e98049\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2a8bdbc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2a8bdbc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Certificati CE, RoHS, SGS<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a7e2c3e elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"a7e2c3e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c801e48 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c801e48\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTutte le macchine Npack sono certificate CE, garantendo la conformit\u00e0 agli standard UE di salute, sicurezza e ambiente. I nostri prodotti aderiscono inoltre alla direttiva RoHS, riflettendo il nostro impegno nella limitazione di sostanze pericolose. La verifica SGS, societ\u00e0 leader in ispezioni e certificazioni, conferma la nostra dedizione a qualit\u00e0, sicurezza e sostenibilit\u00e0. Questa tripla certificazione evidenzia il nostro impegno nel fornire macchinari affidabili e nel rispettare standard internazionali.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa606c8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"aa606c8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9ad32ce elementor-pagination-position-inside elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-carousel\" data-id=\"9ad32ce\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;slides_to_show&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;slides_to_show_tablet&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;slides_to_show_mobile&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;navigation&quot;:&quot;dots&quot;,&quot;autoplay_speed&quot;:3000,&quot;speed&quot;:800,&quot;autoplay&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;pause_on_hover&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;pause_on_interaction&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;infinite&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;effect&quot;:&quot;slide&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image-carousel.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-carousel-wrapper swiper\" role=\"region\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\" aria-label=\"\u56fe\u50cf\u8f6e\u64ad\" dir=\"ltr\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-carousel swiper-wrapper swiper-image-stretch\" aria-live=\"off\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"swiper-slide\" role=\"group\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-label=\"1 di 3\"><figure